  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 14th level, the restraints of the world no longer bind you with its chains. On your turn, you can spend 2 <strong>Martial Die</strong> to give yourself flying speed equal to your movement speed for 1 minute, and can spend 1 <strong>Martial Die</strong> at the end of this duration to restart the duration.</p><p>Also at 14th level, you can use <strong>Unshakeable Will</strong> and <strong>Master of Persistance</strong> without Martial Die, a number of times equal to your Wisdom modifier per long rest.</p>",
